{"type":"message","id":"8c81b70e","parentId":"b02b8912","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:22:24.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of the x402 implementation status:\n\n1. **Implementation Status:**\n   - x402.ts is fully implemented with payment middleware\n   - payment-ledger.ts for tracking payments is implemented\n   - Integration in app.ts is done (x402Guard middleware is applied to paid routes)\n   - Pricing is defined: analyze ($0.01-$0.15), evaluate ($0.01), chat ($0.005)\n\n2. **Git Status:**\n   - x402.ts and payment-ledger.ts are NEW files (untracked - ??)\n   - Several files are modified (M) but not committed\n   - So the x402 implementation has NOT been committed yet\n\n3. **Configuration:**\n   - X402_ENABLED defaults to false in .env.example\n   - Need to set X402_PAY_TO_ADDRESS to enable payments\n   - Uses Base L2 (network eip155:8453) with USDC\n\n4. **Deployment Status:**\n   - There's a Dockerfile and railway.toml, but let me check if it's deployed\n   - The project is separate from parsethe.media (the main Parse site)\n\nLet me check if there's a Railway deployment for parse-for-agents.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me check if this is deployed to Railway."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f4f398642fb444058b43953b","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/kublai/projects/parse-for-agents/railway.toml"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_832e3ac093564c74bfc6afed","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"railway status 2>/dev/null || echo \"Railway CLI not linked or not logged in\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":9257,"output":336,"cacheRead":19200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28793,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772760129837}}
{"type":"message","id":"08a10376","parentId":"8c81b70e","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:22:24.349Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f4f398642fb444058b43953b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[build]\nbuilder = \"DOCKERFILE\"\ndockerfilePath = \"Dockerfile\"\n\n[deploy]\nstartCommand = \"npx tsx src/index.ts\"\nhealthcheckPath = \"/health\"\nhealthcheckTimeout = 30\nrestartPolicyType = \"ON_FAILURE\"\nrestartPolicyMaxRetries = 3\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772760144336}}
