{"type":"message","id":"81bf5548","parentId":"5666c286","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:22:43.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - Railway is linked to the \"parse\" project with a service called \"sunny-perception\". But that might be the main parsethe.media project, not parse-for-agents. Let me check if parse-for-agents has its own Railway project or if it's been deployed.\n\nActually, I should summarize the status for the user now since I have enough information.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Based on my investigation, here's the **status of x402 pay-as-you-go for Parse for Agents**:\n\n## Implementation Status: READY BUT NOT DEPLOYED\n\n### What's Built\n- **x402.ts** — Full payment middleware implementation using `@x402/hono`, `@x402/evm`, and `@x402/core` (v2.5.0)\n- **payment-ledger.ts** — In-memory payment tracking with stats endpoints\n- **Integration** — x402Guard middleware applied to paid routes in app.ts\n\n### Pricing Structure (USDC on Base L2)\n| Endpoint | Price |\n|----------|-------|\n| POST /v1/analyze | $0.01 (quick) / $0.05 (standard) / $0.15 (deep) |\n| POST /v1/evaluate | $0.01 |\n| POST /v1/chat | $0.005 |\n\n### Configuration Required\n```\nX402_ENABLED=true\nX402_PAY_TO_ADDRESS=0x_your_base_wallet_address\n```\n\n### Git Status\n- **x402.ts** and **payment-ledger.ts** are UNTRACKED (not committed)\n- Multiple modified files pending commit\n- Nothing pushed to remote\n\n### Deployment Status\n- Railway project exists (\"parse\") but appears linked to parsethe.media\n- **parse-for-agents is NOT deployed yet**\n\n### Next Steps to Go Live\n1. Set `X402_PAY_TO_ADDRESS` to a Base L2 wallet\n2. Commit and push x402 implementation\n3. Deploy parse-for-agents to Railway (new service or separate project)\n4. Set `X402_ENABLED=true` in Railway environment\n\nWould you like me to route this to Temujin to complete the deployment, or do you want to provide a wallet address first?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":16329,"output":468,"cacheRead":12544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29341,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772760145323}}
